      "weather": "Fine",
      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BLUE WIGGLE (3) has been a little hard to follow, finishing out of the placings latest but was in winning form two back scoring in a Maiden at Taree Super Track. Safe beginner and drawn well close to the inside. Can make amends this time. CHUCKY'S DREAM (1) showed good early burn and was there until turning but swamped late to finish 8th at this track in Grade 5 company. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Better than last start and can bounce back. WILD EXTREME (4) is worth forgiving for her last effort when sixth (23.49) at this track over 400m. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Leading chance. IN THE DARKNESS (2) is right in the mix.",
